 * Direct > SSH2 > FTP Sockets > FTP Extension > PHP Streams. Falls back
 * to `WP_Filesystem_Direct` when the server UID matches the file owner,
 * which is typical for suEXEC, PHP-FPM per-pool, and cPanel jailed shell
